    "error": "ParseError"
}


09. POST /v2/entities with boolean Attribute::name
==================================================
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request
Content-Length: 75
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
Date: REGEX(.*)

{
    "description": "Errors found in incoming JSON buffer", 
    "error": "ParseError"
}


--TEARDOWN--
brokerStop CB
dbDrop CB
